divs: Sighting DetailsThis is a UFO sighting seen at federal heights on just west of 84th and federal. Put your slow motion video camera down and at noon till 1pm MST, a few times a week, these fast moving objects will appear. The UFO(s) are really fast and are really hard to see with the naked eye. Serval news stations started showing up and got footage of this. The UFO appear to take off fast then move around the sky at astonishing speed and possibly land but it's below the tree line so that is unknown. Check it out just google "UFO over Denver" or " mile high UFO sighting". They have professional video equipment catching the event. It's an on going thing. Get your video cameras out and go just west of federal and south of 84th. It's a dirt clearing across from a hospital and shopping center. Point your camera towards Denver around noon MST. Lasts about an hour. Still not sure what it is but it's very unusual.
Summary: Mile High UFO sighting - google it!
